{"tid":338722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"誤診病人致死 退休西醫須賠144萬","createTime":"2017-07-28T11:59:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T02:46:07.000Z","uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3205b6fe8d6da595ea4f2fb96fe96ba0af8eecc3","tid":338722,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T11:59:10.000Z","msg":"曾為兒童注射過期預防流感針的西醫鍾繁生，被指於2012年至2013年半年期間，將一名實際上患甲狀腺功能減退症的病人，誤診為患甲狀腺功能亢進症，並錯誤處方為正常劑量100倍的甲狀腺素予對方服用，最終令對方出現甲狀腺中毒危象，其後死亡。<br />\n<br />\n死者鄧正堂的父親鄧健忠其後以兒子遺產管理人身份，入稟高等法院向鍾繁生索償。法庭早前於鍾沒有抗辯下，裁定鍾須承擔責任，並於今就賠償金額頒下判詞，裁定鍾須賠償144萬元。法官於判詞引述醫療報告指，如果死者獲得正確治療，他將有一半機會完全康復，以及壽命與一般人相約。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1868280/%E8%AA%A4%E8%A8%BA%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E8%87%B4%E6%AD%BB%20%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91%E8%A5%BF%E9%86%AB%E9%A0%88%E8%B3%A0144%E8%90%AC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1868280%2F%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E7%2597%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2587%25B4%25E6%25AD%25BB%2520%25E9%2580%2580%25E4%25BC%2591%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%25A0%2588%25E8%25B3%25A0144%25E8%2590%25AC&d=muqnOp0OfQeuf1dxuKqXo4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=941f6b8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1868280/%E8%AA%A4%E8%A8%BA%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E8%87%B4%E6%AD%BB%20%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91%E8%A5%BF%E9%86%AB%E9%A0%88%E8%B3%A0144%E8%90%AC</a>"},{"pid":"b3008c81204c6537590a5a73c04577465ec00823","tid":338722,"uid":94457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T12:00:43.000Z","msg":"人命何價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace87f38026125bf1488a88512312e5ca2da1b8e","tid":338722,"uid":116718,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T12:02:46.000Z","msg":"咁都係百四萬? 美國告撚到佢破產都得...香港醫療霸權好仆街"},{"pid":"1f16ac85a67f3b254d6d8ec7ed94ce5d0b14389d","tid":338722,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T12:09:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁都係百四萬? 美國告撚到佢破產都得.